hadiths[20]{hadithnumber,text}:
7226,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. agar un logon ka khayal na hota jo mere sath jang mein Sharik na ho sakney ko bura jantey hain magar asbaab ki kami ki wjah se wo Sharik nahi ho saktey aur koi aisi cheez mere paas nahi hai jis par unhein sawar karun to main kabhi ( ghazawaat mein Sharik honey se) peechhey na rahtaa. meri khahish hai ke Allah ke rastey mein qatl kya jaun phir zinda kya jaun, phir qatl kya jaun, phir zinda kya jaun, phir qatl kya jaun , aur phir zinda kya jaun aur phir maara jaun. ''"
7227,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, meri aarzoo hai ke main Allah ke rastey mein jang karun aur qatl kya jaun phir zinda kya jaun , phir qatl kya jaun , phir zinda kya jaun , phir qatl kya jaun , Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) un alfaz ko teen martaba dohraatey they ke main Allah ko gawah karke kehta hoon.''"
7228,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar mere paas Uhud pahaad ke barabar sona hota to main pasand karta ke agar unke leney waley mil jayen to teen din guzarney se pahley hi mere paas usmein se aik Dinar bhi na bachchey , siwa iske jisey main apne uper qarz ki adaaeygi ke liye rok loon. ''"
7229,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par) farmaya ''agar mujh ko apna haal pahley se malum hota jo baad ko malum hua to main apne sath qurbani ka janwar na laataa aur Umra karke doosrey logon ki tarah bhi ehram khol daaltaa.''
7230,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par) sath they, phir ham ne Haj ke liye talbiya kaha aur 4 Zil-Hijja ko Makka pahunchey, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Baitullah aur Safa aur Marwa ke tawaaf ka hukm diya aur ye ke ham usey Umra bana lin aur uske baad halal ho jayen ( siwa unke jinke sath qurbani ka janwar ho wo halal nahi ho saktey ( bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa ham mein se kisi ke paas qurbani ka janwar na tha aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yaman se aaey they aur unke sath bhi hadii thi aur kaha ke main bhi iska ehram baandh kar aaya hun jiska Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram baandha hai, phir doosrey log kehney lagey ke kya ham apni aurton ke sath sohbat karne ke baad Mina ja saktey hain? (is haal mein ke hamarey zakar (khaas ang) mani tapkaatey hon?) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke jo baat mujhey baad mein malum hui agar pahley hi malum hoti to main hadii (qurbaani ka jaanwar) sath na laataa aur agar mere sath hadii na hoti to main bhi halal ho jata. bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Suraqa bin Malik ne mulaqat ki. us waqt aap badey shaitan par rami kar rahe they aur puchha ya Rasulullah ! (kya ( ye hamarey liye khas hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi balke hamesha ke liye hai. bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bhi Makka aai thin lekin wo haaiza thin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein tamam aa'maale-Haj ada karne ka hukm diya, sirf wo paak honey se pahley tawaaf nahi kar sakti thin aur na Namaz padh sakti thin. jab sab log Batha mein utrey to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! kya aap sab log Umra w Haj donon karke lauteingey aur mera sirf Haj hoga? bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke Aaisha ko sath lekar maqam taneem jaaein. chunanche unhon-ne bhi ayyaame-Haj ke baad Zil-Hijja mein Umra kya."
7231,"aik raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko neend na aai , phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' kash! mere sahaba mein se koi nek mard mere liye aaj raat pahra deta.'' itney mein ham ne hathiyaaron ki awaz suni. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kon sahib hain? bataya gaya ke Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) hain ya Rasulullah ! ( unhon-ne kaha ( mein aap ke liye pahra dene aaya hun, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) soey yahan tak ke ham ne aap ke kharraatey ki awaz suni. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) jab naey naey Madina aaey to bukhar aur hairaanii ki haalat mein ye sher padhtey they. ''kaash main janta ke main aik raat us wadi mein guzaar sakunga .) wadi mein) aur mere charon taraf izkhir aur jaleel ghaas hogi. '' phir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uski khabar ki."
7232,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' rashk sirf 2 shakhson par ho sakta hai aik wo jisey Allah ne Quran diya hai aur wo usey din raat padhta rehta hai aur is par) sunney wala ( kahey ke agar mujhey bhi iska aisa hi ilm hota jaisa ke us shakhs ko diya gaya hai to main bhi isi tarah karta jaisa ke ye karta hai aur doosra wo shakhs jisey Allah ne maal diya aur wo usey Allah ke rastey mein kharch karta hai to ( dekhney wala ( kahey ke agar mujhey bhi itna diya jata jaisa usey diya gaya hai to main bhi isi tarah karta jaisa ke ye kar raha hai.'' ham se Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Jarir ne phir yahi hadis bayan ki."
7233,agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye na suna hota ke maut ki tamanna na karo to main maut ki aarzoo karta.
7234,"ham Khabbaab-bin-Arat (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein unki iyaadat ke liye hazir huey. unhon-ne saat (7) dagh lagwaaey they, phir unhon-ne kaha ke agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein maut ki dua karne se mana na kya hota to main uski dua karta."
7235,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii shakhs tum mein se maut ki aarzoo na karey, agar wo nek hai to mumkin hai neki main aur zyada ho aur agar bura hai to mumkin hai us se tauba kar ley.''"
7236,"Khandaq ki jang ke din (khandaq khodtey huey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi khud hamarey sath mitti uthaya kartey they. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is haal mein dekha ke mitti ne aap ke pet ki safedi ko chipa diya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ''agar to na hota (aey Allah ! ( to ham na hidayat patey , na ham sadqa detey, na Namaz padhtey . to ham par dil-jamaii nazil farmaa. us dushman ki jamaat ne hamarey khilaf had se aagey badh kar hamla kya hai. jab ye fitna chahtey hain to ham unki baat nahi maantey, nahi maantey. is par aap awaz ko buland kar detey. ''"
7237,Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein likha aur maine usey padha to usmein ye mazmoon tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai ke dushman se mudbhed honey ki tamanna na karo aur Allah se aafiyat ki dua maanga karo.
7238,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne 2 liaan karne walon ka zikr kya to is par Abdullaah-bin-Shaddaad ne puchha : kya yahi wo hain jinke mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke ''agar main kisi aurat ko baghair gawah ke rajm (sangsaar) kar sakta to isey kartaa.'' Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke nahi wo aik (aur ( aurat thi jo (Islam laney ke baad) khuley aam ( fahash kaam ( karti thi.
7239,"aik raat aisa hua Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha ki Namaz mein der ki. aakhir umr (Raziallahu anhu) nikley aur kehney lagey ya Rasulullah ! Namaz padhiye auratein aur bachchey soney lagey. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (hujrey se) baraamad huey aap ke sar se pani tapak raha tha (ghusl karke bahar tashrif laey ( farmaney lagey agar meri ummat par ya yun farmaya ke logon par dushwar na hota. Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne yun kaha ke meri ummat par dushwar na hota to main is waqt (itni raat gaey) unko ye Namaz padhney ka hukm deta aur ibne-Juraij ne (isii sanad se Sufiyan se, unhon-ne (ibne-Juraij se) unhon-ne Ata se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us Namaz (yani isha ki Namaz mein der ki. umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur kehney lagey ya Rasulullah ! auratein bachchey so gaey. ye sun kar aap bahar tashrif laaey, apne sar ki aik taraf se pani poonchh rahe they, farma rahe they is Namaz ka (umda ( waqt yahi hai agar meri ummat par sakht na ho. Amr-bin-Dinar ne is hadis mein yun naql kya. ham se Ata ne bayan kya aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahi kya lekin Amr ne yun kaha aap ke sar se pani tapak raha tha aur ibne-Juraij ki riwayat mein yun hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sar ke aik taraf se pani poonchh rahe they. aur Amr ne kaha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar meri ummat par sakht na hota aur ibne-Juraij ne kaha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar meri ummat par sakht na hota to is Namaz ka ( afzal ( waqt to yahi hai. aur Ibrahim bin al-Munzir (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke Shekh ( ne kaha ham se Ma'n (معن) bin Esa ne bayan kya, kaha mujh se Muhammad-bin Muslim ne, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-abi-Ribah se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se phir yahi hadis naql ki."
7240,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar meri ummat par sakht na hota to main un par miswak karna wajib qarar deta.''
7241,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan ke aakhiri dinon mein saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) rakha to kuchh sahaba ne bhi saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) rakha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko iski itlaa mili to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar is mahiney ke din aur badh jatey to main itney din mutwaatir wisaal karta ke hawas karne waley apni hawas chhod detey, main tum logon jaisa nahi hun. main is tarah din guzaarta hun ke mera rab mujhey khilata pilaataa hai. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne ki, unse Sabit ne, unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne, unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa farmaya jo uper mazkoor hua."
7242,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saume-wisaal (raat-din lagaataar roza rakhne) se mana kya to sahaba ne kaha ke aap to wisaal kartey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein kon mujh jaisa hai, main to is haal mein raat guzaarta hun ke mera rab mujhey khilata pilaataa hai lekin jab log na maaney to aap ne aik din ke sath doosra din mila kar) wisaal ka ( roza rakha , phir logon ne ( eid ka ( chaand dekha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar chaand na hota to main aur wisaal karta, maano Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein tanbeeh karne ke liye aisa farmaya,"
7243,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (khaana Kaba ke) Hateem ke barey mein puchha ke kya ye bhi khaana Kaba ka hissa hai? farmaya ke haan. maine kaha : phir kyon un logon ne usey Baitullah mein dakhil nahi kiya? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhari qaum ke paas kharch ki kami ho gaee thi, maine kaha ke ye khaana Kaba ka darwaza oonchaaii par kyon hai? farmaya ke ye isliye unhon-ne kya hai taake jisey chaahein andar dakhil karein aur jisey chaahein rok dein. agar tumhari qaum ( Quraish (ka zamana jahiliyat se qareeb na hota aur mujhey khof na hota ke unke dilon mein us se inkar paida hoga to main Hateem ko bhi khaana Kaba mein shamil kar deta aur uske darwazey ko zameen ke barabar kar deta."
7244,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar hijrat (ki fazeelat ( na hoti to main Ansar ka aik fard bannaa ( pasand karta (aur agar doosrey log kisi wadi mein chalein aur Ansar aik wadi ya ghaati mein chalein to main Ansar ki wadi ya ghaati mein chaloonga.''
7245,"agar hijrat na hoti to main Ansar ka aik fard hota aur agar log kisi wadi ya ghaati mein chalein to main Ansar ki wadi ya ghaati mein chaloonga. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Abu-Tayyah ne ki, unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. usmein bhi darrey ka zikr hai."
